title: How Your Brain Affects Your Relationships
itunes:title: How Your Brain Affects Your Relationships
description:
Episode 484 - This is a long one, but a GOOD one! In this episode, John Howard, an amazing relationship therapist, and I dive into how your first relationships as a child affect every relationship you will have the rest of your life. We have some deep psychological conversations and I guarantee you will learn a lot!
